{"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"copy"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This string is displayed in the callout for the associated annotation.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"title":"subtitle","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)subtitle","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/subtitle":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","title":"subtitle","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"}}}